<h1>Facebook Ads Dashboard PRD</h1>
<p class="subtitle">One-Page Product Requirements Document | Version 2.1 | January 2026</p>

<h2>1. What is This Application?</h2>
<p>A unified dashboard to <strong>track, analyze, and optimize</strong> Facebook Ads performance for Pabbly products. Unlike Facebook Ads Manager, this dashboard:</p>
<ul>
<li>Combines Facebook ad metrics with <strong>actual sales revenue</strong> from our payment system</li>
<li>Sends conversion data back to Facebook via <strong>Conversion API (CAPI)</strong> for better ad optimization</li>
<li>Provides <strong>smart alerts</strong> to increase/decrease budgets (Facebook doesn't offer this)</li>
<li>Shows <strong>country-wise performance</strong> with real revenue data</li>
</ul>

