</table>

<h2>9. Settings</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Facebook Connection:</strong> View connected accounts, sync status</li>
<li><strong>CAPI Settings:</strong> Configure Conversion API pixel ID and access token</li>
<li><strong>Alert Thresholds:</strong> Set ROAS limits, spend limits, frequency limits</li>
<li><strong>Webhooks:</strong> Create endpoints for receiving external data</li>
<li><strong>User Management:</strong> Admin, Editor, Viewer roles</li>
</ul>

